<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='313416' id='t-313416'>And of course, the name of the giant is Goliath</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='317777' id='t-317777'>and the name of the shepherd boy is David,</span>
