<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='330717' id='t-330717'>So David, in that story, is supposed to be the underdog, right?</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='334505' id='t-334505'>In fact, that term, David and Goliath,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='336642' id='t-336642'>has entered our language as a metaphor for</span>
