<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='344272' id='t-344272'>Now why do we call David an underdog?</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='346462' id='t-346462'>Well, we call him an underdog because he's a kid,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='349937' id='t-349937'>a little kid, and Goliath is this big, strong giant.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='353473' id='t-353473'>We also call him an underdog</span>
