<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='375962' id='t-375962'>and all David has is this sling.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 6:30
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='379792' id='t-379792'>Well, let's start there with the phrase</span>
