<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='383934' id='t-383934'>because that's the first mistake that we make.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='386801' id='t-386801'>In ancient warfare, there are three kinds of warriors.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='390358' id='t-390358'>There's cavalry, men on horseback and with chariots.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='393789' id='t-393789'>There's heavy infantry, which are foot soldiers,</span>
