<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='436905' id='t-436905'>It's in fact an incredibly devastating weapon.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='440730' id='t-440730'>When David rolls it around like this,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='443706' id='t-443706'>he's turning the sling around probably</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='446935' id='t-446935'>at six or seven revolutions per second,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='449607' id='t-449607'>and that means that when the rock is released,</span>
