<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='580697' id='t-580697'>But David has absolutely no expectation.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='583671' id='t-583671'>He's not going to fight him that way. Why would he?</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='586222' id='t-586222'>He's a shepherd. He's spent his entire career</span>
