<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='593443' id='t-593443'>That's where his strength lies.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='595193' id='t-595193'>So here he is, this shepherd, experienced</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='597725' id='t-597725'>in the use of a devastating weapon,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='599764' id='t-599764'>up against this lumbering giant</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='602158' id='t-602158'>weighed down by a hundred pounds of armor</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='605458' id='t-605458'>and these incredibly heavy weapons</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='606959' id='t-606959'>that are useful only in short-range combat.</span>
