<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='684940' id='t-684940'>And then there's this whole weird thing</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='686763' id='t-686763'>about how long it takes Goliath to react</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='690575' id='t-690575'>to the sight of David.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='692571' id='t-692571'>So David's coming down the mountain,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='695349' id='t-695349'>and he's clearly not preparing for hand-to-hand combat.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='699286' id='t-699286'>There is nothing about him that says,</span>
