<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='703288' id='t-703288'>He's not even carrying a sword.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='705019' id='t-705019'>Why does Goliath not react to that?</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='707701' id='t-707701'>It's as if he's oblivious to what's going on that day.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='711929' id='t-711929'>And then there's that strange comment he makes to David:</span>
